These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-1::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: march, july, december, august, may, january, june
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: azalea, aconite, amaryllis, sunflower, rose, bellflower, orchid
 1. the person who growsorchid is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 2. the person who growsazalea is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##8
 3. the person who growsazalea is not to the left of the person who growsaconite##8
 4. the person who growsaconite is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the left of the person who growsbellflower##8
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is not the person who growsaconite##6
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##8
 9. the person who growsrose is somewhere between the person who growsorchid and the person who growsaconite##7
10. the person who growsaconite is the person who's birthday is in january##1
11. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
12. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
13. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
14. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere between the person who growsrose and the person who growsazalea##7
15. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
16. the person who growsbellflower is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##8
17. the person who growsorchid is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
18. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who growsamaryllis##1
19. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
20. the person who's birthday is in august is not the person who growsbellflower##6
21. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##8
22. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |      3       |    4    |    5     |      6      |    7    |
| Birthday           | january | december | june | july  | may  | august | march    |
| Flower   | aconite   | azalea   | amaryllis   | sunflower | rose | orchid        | bellflower |

